          "title": "Heat Illness Prevention Monitoring Log",
          "html": "<p><strong>Topic/Subject: </strong>Heat Illness Prevention Monitoring Log</p>\n<p><strong>Trainer/Presenter: </strong>______________________________________________________</p>\n<p><strong>Training Content Summary:</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"sec-list\"><li class=\"sec-bullet\">• Review of heat illness signs and symptoms (heat exhaustion vs. heat stroke)</li><li class=\"sec-bullet\">• Importance of hydration, shade, and rest breaks</li><li class=\"sec-bullet\">• Emergency response procedures for heat-related illnesses</li><li class=\"sec-bullet\">• Monitoring environmental conditions and adjusting work schedules</li><li class=\"sec-bullet\">• Buddy system implementation for monitoring co-workers</li></ul>"
